text.__SUMMARY__: Psychotria cyathicalyx is a species of plant in the family Rubiaceae. It is endemic to Tanzania.
text.Sources: Lovett, J. & Clarke, G.P. (1998). "Psychotria cyathicalyx". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T35459A9934103. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T35459A9934103.en. Retrieved 19 December 2017.
